 {"id":"bd-2gkx","title":"Reliability + UX enhancements from docs","description":"Objective: implement accretive reliability/UX improvements surfaced in docs (DEGRADATION, module-map, robot-mode-api, coverage-matrix) without disrupting existing functionality. Focus on tool health resilience, event loss visibility, dependency-aware diagnostics, and richer operator UX. Ensure all changes include unit + integration + E2E tests with detailed logging/diagnostics.","status":"open","priority":2,"issue_type":"epic","created_at":"2026-01-27T21:34:00.227214272Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-01-27T21:34:00.227214272Z","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0}
 {"id":"bd-2gkx.1","title":"Circuit breaker for tool health checks","description":"Implement a circuit breaker layer for repeated tool health checks (DCG, NTM, br, bv, cass, cm, ru, etc.) to avoid noisy repeated failures. Cache failure state with exponential backoff and cool-down, expose breaker status in /health/ready and tool registry metadata, and log state transitions with correlation IDs. Tests: unit tests for breaker state machine + integration tests simulating repeated failures; E2E readiness check validates degraded vs unhealthy states with detailed logs.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-27T21:34:12.511384909Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-01-29T05:06:33.588436198Z","closed_at":"2026-01-29T05:06:33.588368812Z","close_reason":"Circuit breaker service with CLOSED/OPEN/HALF_OPEN state machine, exponential backoff (30s-5min), per-tool configuration, and withCircuitBreaker() wrapper. Integrated into /health/detailed for DCG/CASS/UBS checks. 19 passing unit tests. Breaker status exposed in health response.","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-2gkx.1","depends_on_id":"bd-2gkx","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-01-29T04:21:46Z","created_by":"import"},{"issue_id":"bd-2gkx.1","depends_on_id":"bd-2gkx.4","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-01-29T04:21:46Z","created_by":"import"}]}
 {"id":"bd-2gkx.10","title":"E2E: reliability + diagnostics flows","description":"Add Playwright E2E scenarios for new reliability features: circuit breaker state changes, event-loss banner, dependency-aware health diagnostics, and unified error labels. Require the E2E logging framework + runner and capture traces/screenshots/WS logs. Success: reliability UX is validated end-to-end with rich diagnostics.","status":"open","priority":3,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-27T21:35:25.650413452Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-01-27T21:37:30.223772755Z","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-2gkx.10","depends_on_id":"bd-1vr1.10","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-01-29T04:21:46Z","created_by":"import"},{"issue_id":"bd-2gkx.10","depends_on_id":"bd-1vr1.5","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-01-29T04:21:46Z","created_by":"import"},{"issue_id":"bd-2gkx.10","depends_on_id":"bd-2gkx","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-01-29T04:21:46Z","created_by":"import"},{"issue_id":"bd-2gkx.10","depends_on_id":"bd-2gkx.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-01-29T04:21:46Z","created_by":"import"},{"issue_id":"bd-2gkx.10","depends_on_id":"bd-2gkx.2","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-01-29T04:21:46Z","created_by":"import"},{"issue_id":"bd-2gkx.10","depends_on_id":"bd-2gkx.3","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-01-29T04:21:46Z","created_by":"import"},{"issue_id":"bd-2gkx.10","depends_on_id":"bd-2gkx.4","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-01-29T04:21:46Z","created_by":"import"}]}
