+{"id":"bd-2gkx.2","title":"WebSocket event loss telemetry + client alerts","description":"Add explicit event-loss notifications when WS ring buffers or throttlers drop messages. Emit counters/metrics, include last-drop timestamps, and publish a system:events channel message so UI can display a warning banner. Tests: unit tests for drop detection + serialization; integration tests verifying client receives loss notice; E2E test validates banner + logs with traces.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-27T21:34:18.703632899Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-01-29T05:10:31.523556478Z","closed_at":"2026-01-29T05:10:31.523488341Z","close_reason":"Added RingBufferDropStats with capacity eviction and TTL expiration counters. Hub aggregates per-buffer stats into HubStats.eventLoss with totalCapacityEvictions, totalTtlExpirations, totalSendFailures, lastDropAt, and byChannel breakdown. Send failures counted in publish(). 7 passing unit tests.","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-2gkx.2","depends_on_id":"bd-2gkx","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-01-29T04:21:46Z","created_by":"import"}]}
 {"id":"bd-2gkx.3","title":"Dependency-aware health diagnostics","description":"Add dependency analysis to /health/ready and tool registry metadata so failures show root causes (e.g., NTM unavailable because tmux missing; br unavailable because Rust toolchain missing). Model tool dependencies via ACFS manifest tags/depends, compute causal chains, and expose structured diagnostics. Tests: unit tests for dependency graph analysis + integration tests for readiness payloads; E2E verifies UI renders dependency explanations with detailed logs.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-27T21:34:26.767817476Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-01-29T05:00:08.376377105Z","closed_at":"2026-01-29T05:00:08.376304370Z","close_reason":"Implemented dependency-aware diagnostics with graph traversal, cascade failure detection, and /health/detailed integration. 8 tests passing.","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-2gkx.3","depends_on_id":"bd-2gkx","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-01-29T04:21:46Z","created_by":"import"},{"issue_id":"bd-2gkx.3","depends_on_id":"bd-2gkx.4","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-01-29T04:21:46Z","created_by":"import"},{"issue_id":"bd-2gkx.3","depends_on_id":"bd-2n73.2","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-01-29T04:21:46Z","created_by":"import"}]}
 {"id":"bd-2gkx.4","title":"Unified tool unavailability taxonomy + error mapping","description":"Standardize tool-unavailable errors across services (detection, health, tool clients). Define a shared error taxonomy (e.g., NOT_INSTALLED, PERMISSION_DENIED, VERSION_UNSUPPORTED, AUTH_REQUIRED, MCP_UNREACHABLE), map CLI exit codes and stderr patterns, and ensure consistent HTTP codes and UI labels. Tests: unit tests for classification rules + integration tests across services; E2E verifies UI badges and error details with structured logs.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-27T21:34:36.729969036Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-01-29T04:28:55.861587375Z","closed_at":"2026-01-29T04:28:55.861515301Z","close_reason":"Implemented unified tool unavailability taxonomy with 14 canonical reasons, stderr pattern classifier, exit code mapping, HTTP status/UI label metadata, auto-classification in CliClientError, DetectedCLI integration, 13 new ErrorCodes with AI hints, and 35 unit tests.","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-2gkx.4","depends_on_id":"bd-2gkx","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-01-29T04:21:46Z","created_by":"import"}]}
 {"id":"bd-2gkx.5","title":"Snapshot + metrics expansion for tool ecosystem","description":"Expand snapshot/metrics coverage to include NTM, CASS, CM, RU, SLB, UBS, CAAM, MS, PT, RCH, and other new utilities. Define per-tool health metrics, last-seen versions, and auth state. Surface in system snapshot API and UI. Tests: unit tests for snapshot aggregation; integration tests verifying metrics emission; E2E snapshot view with detailed logging.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-27T21:34:45.422686476Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-01-29T04:49:37.915160309Z","closed_at":"2026-01-29T04:49:37.915083266Z","close_reason":"Expanded ToolHealthSnapshot with ecosystem detection (all agents + tools from ACFS manifest). Added ToolEcosystemSummary and DetectedToolSummary types, integrated detectAllCLIs() into snapshot collection, added per-tool metrics emission, and 3 type-level tests.","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-2gkx.5","depends_on_id":"bd-2gkx","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-01-29T04:21:46Z","created_by":"import"},{"issue_id":"bd-2gkx.5","depends_on_id":"bd-2n73.3","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-01-29T04:21:46Z","created_by":"import"},{"issue_id":"bd-2gkx.5","depends_on_id":"bd-2n73.4","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-01-29T04:21:46Z","created_by":"import"}]}
